<plot>Tony (Govinda) works as a guide, helping tourists, and showing them his native land. Nina (Namrata Shirodkar) finds Tony adorable, but Tony is in his own world, and does not reciprocate her attentions. When Sonia (Aishwarya Rai) for a tour of the surroundings, and is immediately taken-up with Tony and his easy manner. Tony mistakes this for love, and is smitten by her beauty. But Sonia already has a sweetheart, and so what will convince him that Sonia does not have similar feelings for him?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?028880</url></doc>
